---
title: Pan-Seared Pork Chops with Onion Gravy, Broccoli and Buttery Mash
description: An ideal meal after a long day. This rosemary-seasoned, gravy-smothered pork dish is perfection. Roasted broccoli and mashed potatoes top off this dish for a comfort food extravaganza! Bon appetit!
